Detailed Description

Instruction semantics policy for API-compliant function calls.

The main thing this does differently from FindConstantsPolicy is that x86 CALL instructions initialize the register set and memory for the instruction at the next address after the CALL assuming that the called function will honor the ABI specification and will return to the address following the CALL.
